This directory contains API schema files which have been converted from an older
schema format to the more modern WebIDL format. When a conversion is done, the
original old schema file is moved here and a copy of the new WebIDL file is
added. The file pair is then added to the `web_idl_diff_tool_test.py` file, in
order to have a verifiable test run in the CL that converts the schema, which
shows there is no functional difference in the output from the old and new file
after processing.

This means these file should not be updated with any subsequent changes to the
WebIDL schema that might come in the future, as they are meant to represent that
there was no difference at the time of conversion. There is a PRESUBMIT in place
to help enforce this, which gives a warning on upload if any edits have been
made to the schema files (additions and deletions are okay). It is expected that
these schemas will diverge from the actual schemas over time.

Eventually once enough of the schema files have been converted, these files and
the test entries can be deleted. However, while the conversion process is still
ongoing, they are useful to pick up on subtle regressions that might come from
additions to the WebIDL processor, letting us add specific test cases for them
to the actual `web_idl_schema_test.py` test cases.
